**Tony Lopez** is a French videographer who has been touring big festivals across Europe for rappers and artists. He created his own style mixing live reports with 3D animations and high-quality video editing. With covid and lockdown, he finally found time to get more into 3D and started creating dreamy environments with a surreal style. He found in 3D a beautiful way to express his creativity and to open the minds of others.
&nbsp;
He now spends every day creating what he imagines and sharing it with the world pushing the boundaries of creativity.

drops.description:
"*Protect the Jellyfishes*" is a 3D animated collection that contains 3 surreal visuals, mixing beautiful environments with the great movements of the Jellyfishes. The 3 animated visuals represent our actual Hell, Earth, and Heaven. Tony has been inspired by the image of flying jellyfishes if they weren't underwater animals because of their gracious movements, which he finds soothing. In addition to these visuals, the Jellyfish Coin animation is created with exclusive materials, with the light going through, like Jellyfish skin.
&nbsp;

Every visual has been worked with the producer @jstbenmusic for more immersive pieces.

drops.creatorInfo:
With over 11 million likes on Tiktok (@augurusae), **Eric Augurusa** is among the fastest-growing Canadian visual artists in the industry. Inspired by his personal struggles and love towards the NFT community, **Eric** has formed a talented collective featuring visual and music artists from Germany, Switzerland, Italy, Singapore and the USA to bring you an audiovisual collection called "*Your Personal Journey*".What connects the collective is the desire to master each of our own respective journeys and provide inspiration to the viewer to join us in doing so.
&nbsp;

The idea for this project came about 2 months ago when we noticed a trend towards NFT art pieces that focused more on the graphics of the piece, but not any particular emotion or feeling. Naturally, we asked ourselves what could we create that we would like to own and find meaning in. From the start, we wanted to emphasize that the collection is about the viewer and that the viewer would benefit from "getting lost" in the art pieces. We hope we achieved that.

drops.description:
"*Your Personal Journey*" aims to provide you with the inspiration to withstand hardship, increase your courage and trust in the universe, learn to build serenity within yourself even if the world is crumbling down, appreciate your loved ones and inspire you to take on adventures that the universe has in store for you. 
&nbsp;

Often times we fall into the crippling abyss of confusion, doubt, and pain, but in those moments all you need is a simple reminder that you're transitioning into a stronger and wiser version of yourself who's ready to take on challenges deemed impossible by your past versions. All it takes is to open your mind to the opportunities that await to pull you out of the mental slump. We hope our carefully designed audiovisual art pieces accomplish this important task. All we ask is that you return to your chosen artwork next time you are feeling down. From the bottom of our hearts, we wish you an amazing journey.
&nbsp;
In total, there are 5 different pieces distributed amongst 100 surprise art packs. These pieces are minted with varying levels of rarity; the first, 30 editions will be made, the second, 25 editions, the third and fourth, 20 editions  — but five lucky art collectors will receive a rare 5/5 creation. Generated at random, and available for $500 each, the packs will each include 1 piece of collectible art — which can be virtually unwrapped and kept or traded on the Crypto.com/NFT marketplace.

drops.creatorInfo:
**Gareth Bale** is a globally recognized professional football player who plays for thirteen-time European champions Real Madrid & represents the Welsh national team serving as their captain. Bale began his professional career at Southampton, playing at left-back and earning acclaim as a free-kick specialist. Bale moved to Tottenham Hotspur in 2007, where managerial and tactical shifts saw him transform into an attacking player.
&nbsp;

In 2011 and 2013 he was named PFA Players' Player of the Year, and was named in the UEFA Team of the Year. In 2013, he was also named PFA Young Player of the Year, the FWA Footballer of the Year, and the Premier League Player of the Season. He was nominated to the PFA Team of the Year three times in a row between 2011 and 2013.  Gareth joined Real Madrid on September 1st, 2013 for a then world-record transfer fee of €100.8 million, eclipsing the previous record the club had paid for Cristiano Ronaldo in 2009.
&nbsp;

Bale played an integral role in his first season at Real Madrid, helping the club to win the 2013–14 Copa del Rey and UEFA Champions League, scoring in both finals. The following season, he won the UEFA Super Cup and scored in a third major final to help the club win the FIFA Club World Cup. Two years later, he was a key player in another Champions League run, winning the 2015–16 title and being elected to the UEFA Squad of the Season.
&nbsp;

In one of the most memorable moments in football history, Gareth scored the winner with a stunning overhead kick in the 2018 European Champions League Final - a goal widely regarded as one of the greatest Champions League goals of all time. Bale made his senior international debut for Wales in May 2006, becoming the youngest player at that point to represent Wales. He has since earned over 90 caps and scored 33 international goals, making him Wales' highest scorer of all time. He has been named Welsh Footballer of the Year a record six times.

**Matthew Medney** is the CEO of the legendary **Heavy Metal Magazine** and co-founded boutique storytelling company Herø Projects, where he also still presides as CEO. Leading the charge at two genre focused brands, Matthew spends most of his time thinking about the unknown.
&nbsp;

A graduate of the University Of Massachusetts at Amherst's Isenberg School of Management, Matthew started his career in the live events space — operating as a tour and production manager, traveling across 45 countries and producing over 200 shows for concerts such as Coachella, Ultra Music Festival, Electric Daisy Carnival and Lollapalooza. "A prolific writer" (Variety) with the ultimate goal of looking to expand minds and engage readers through high concept science fiction, Medney has authored best selling works such as his hard sci-fi novel "Beyond Kuiper: The Galactic Star Alliance" and the graphic novel "Dark Wing." In addition, he has penned multiple comic books including "The Red" and his highly-anticipated forthcoming work "The Adventures of Adrienne James," which can best be described as "female Indiana Jones — in space" (SYFY).
&nbsp;
Other notable comic and graphic novel works Medney has helmed include work done in collaboration with bands and music festivals such as the largest hip-hop festival in the world, Rolling Loud, Grammy-winning musician Shaggy, along with other notable talents such as NGHTMRE, Pegboard Nerds, Riot and Insomniac Events.
&nbsp;
**John Connelly** is a Mechanical Engineer for Lockheed Martin Space, who contributes to numerous NASA missions, including Mars 2020, LUCY, Deep Space Gateway, and Orion; however, space and the unknown don’t occupy his entire being. Following his dreams to work in the aerospace industry, John moved to Denver, Colorado where he met Tony, his amazing wine slinging partner, who is a Chef and Sommelier. John’s expansive mind and energetic curiosity led him to enjoy a myriad of creative outlets, such as boulder scrambling, disc golf, searching for the perfect wave to body surf, gardening peppers too hot to eat, and gloving. Between delving into these fine activities, he honors his Irish heritage and cardio needs by participating in Ireland’s true traditional sport: hurling (look it up). Beyond all this, he is an artist, an acrylic painter, whose strokes transcribe exotic dreamscapes to canvas and bring a vibrant lush palette to illuminate new worlds.
&nbsp;
Throughout all of these diverse facets of life, his affinity for words never wavered. Transcribed and translated from existential questions to tangible adventure, his and Matt’s world building and galactic lore span a lifetime of curiosity. 
&nbsp;
[*Read more about the collection and preview some of the pieces on our blog.*](https://medium.com/cryptocomnft/heavy-metal-will-transport-nft-collectors-to-fantastical-new-worlds-fe0ad62faf7c)

