Known for viral series like icons unmasked, as well as working with clients like One Piece, General Mills, Timberland, Tekashi 69, Hilton, Sanrio and others. Excited to focus more on NFT independent projects! **Alex Solis** currently resides in Wisconsin where he works full time on his own brand Oddworx. When he’s not working on art, he spends most of his time with his family.
